  DEAD KINGS, AN ALL-NEW CAMPAIGN
 
  Saint Denis, 1794. Following the events of AssassinÃ†s Creed Unity, journey
  with Arno to the ominous rural city of Saint Denis. Follow him as Arno
  explores the troubling open-world city of Saint Denis and its extensive
  underground universe ? an ancient necropolis with an intricate network of
  catacombs and deep caves that hide the best-kept secrets of the French kings.
 
  Use ArnoÃ†s lantern to advance in the dark, fend off the animals creeping
  around the catacombs, and solve ancestral puzzles. Alternatively, put out
  the lantern and become one with the shadows.
 
  Unlock the powerful new Guillotine Gun to unleash both explosive destruction
  and close-combat havoc.
